---
---
^cat <<End_Of_CCM_Conf > /etc/ccm.conf$
^profile https://somewhere/node_profile$
^key_file /path/to/key$
^cert_file /path/to/cert$
^ca_file /path/to/ca$
^world_readable 0$
^dbformat myformat$
^trust MY@TRUST$
^End_Of_CCM_Conf$
^/usr/sbin/ccm-initialise \|\| fail
^/usr/sbin/ccm-fetch \|\| fail
